{"tid":280540,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"寫左隻Web Crawler集中公營機構嘅職位空缺,你問我答","createTime":"2017-06-12T07:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T09:40:15.000Z","uid":35211,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa93dc80de5f972ba44b3eff63c557a8af91def","tid":280540,"uid":35211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fjobs.yakoo.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffjobs.yakoo.com.hk&d=R6ovdL9rzY5bByH2AfPvFsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f9912efc\" target=\"_blank\">https://fjobs.yakoo.com.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n個網址係自已公司subdomain,放出黎基本上係自爆,不過一向CD ROM無乜所謂.<br />\n其實一早寫好左,不過一直唔滿意所以放置PLAY.近來為左練coding重新寫左一次,放出黎睇下對其他人有冇用.<br />\n功能基本上係簡陋都乜都冇,有人覺得用先再算~"},{"pid":"25abca41a6b89eba27d708998ea7a0b2be93a3d0","tid":280540,"uid":101991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"近排都睇緊web crawling , support"},{"pid":"7e312df988056c7b3e4484651d6970fa6e9c7508","tid":280540,"uid":35211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:11:31.000Z","msg":"自推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88de5edee289d4695f084f2aa1c655f97cffca3f","tid":280540,"uid":70002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:19:13.000Z","msg":"同政府個app 有咩唔同？<br />\n<br />\n整個crawl 全港 mt<br />\n或者bank 呢d 會唔會大d gimmick?"},{"pid":"acca4d086fd716316dca7a1480c8d5619f7bce48","tid":280540,"uid":58249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"67b2b82e8ae1047ef98976c455ea5b7e6a8e638b","tid":280540,"uid":70002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"你逐個website 拆佢structure?"},{"pid":"b7349eae7f955a4320c7d29175ed9735c1a4acb2","tid":280540,"uid":35211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:00:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你逐個website 拆佢structure?</blockquote><b