ssets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傾下計當幫推ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我學緊寫crawler<br />\n有無咩地方要注意?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e6c07b7a35deebd21ef8b80483dd3aa209893b","tid":280540,"uid":35211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自推埋呢個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傾下計當幫推ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我學緊寫crawler<br />\n有無咩地方要注意?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最Basic就係要知道HTTP Request除左URL之外仲有好多野. <br />\n想扮Browser過BotCheck 最起碼係要set User-Agent.如果D site 有CSRF protection 有時仲要扮Cookie/先攞一次token之類."},{"pid":"d443da4d51847f58ebdb7f3abc071edf4e7d2c57","tid":280540,"uid":35211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:14:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個網站幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝巴打<br />\n但我想問網頁版有無save job 既功能？</blockquote><br />\n其實都想做返save job，但唔想做開acc之類，大概都係會跟機跟broswer</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新加左bookmark功能，不過d UI擺位仲要再執執"},{"pid":"85eed3302812fa7261cf1e0b151a9bc0eeae51de","tid":280540,"uid":66975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個網站幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝巴打<br />\n但我想問網頁版有無save job 既功能？</blockquote><br />\n其實都想做返save job，但唔想做開acc之類，大概都係會跟機跟broswer</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\"